kubectl describe limitrange <name>           # Get details
kubectl top pods                              # Show pod resource usage
kubectl top nodes                             # Show node resource usage
```

## RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)

### RBAC Commands
```bash
kubectl get roles                             # List all roles
kubectl get rolebindings                      # List all role bindings
kubectl get clusterroles                      # List cluster roles
kubectl get clusterrolebindings               # List cluster role bindings
